snippet.title: Let's Play Legend of the River King 2 01: A Fishy Adventure
snippet.description:
Welcome to Let's Play Legend of the River King 2, in this episode, we begin our search for the River King through fishing up some tiny fish. 

Be sure to keep up with updates on twitter: https://twitter.com/Thomal9
